# Design drafts. Deploys here upload the WORKING TREE, not git, so an
# untracked scratch folder still ships — without this, /mockups/*.html is
# publicly reachable on the client-facing site. Caught on the 2026-07-22
# deploy, where the folder had to be moved aside by hand to keep drafts off
# production.
